details.name: Street Race - Beachfront Runner
details.creator: RSGIND_CastroA
details.desc: You know how to party in Del Perro. Beat LS's legendary drivers in a breakneck street race, slam some cocktails at Bahama Mamas, blackout on the dancefloor, and wake up spewing cotton candy on Pleasure Pier. Time to initiate phase one. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
